Update run.sh with needed env variables

Needed env variables:
    POSTGRES_USER,
    POSTGRES_PASSWORD,
    POSTGRES_DB

build docker images with `docker build ./api/`
build docker images with `docker build ./db/`

run `./run.sh` to start the sensor db and server in docker containers

Quick bash startup script:
```
export POSTGRES_USER=
export POSTGRES_PASSWORD=
export POSTGRES_DB=

{repo_path}/scripts/run.sh
```

